
eXist Native XML Database - Version 0.9
=======================================

For instructions on how to install and start eXist, please
refer to the QuickStart.html document contained in this
directory. Alternatively you may directly start the included
Tomcat webserver and read the documentation which will be 
available at

http://localhost:8080/exist/index.xml.

To start Tomcat and eXist, set your JAVA_HOME and EXIST_HOME
environment variables to point to the directory of your Java
installation and the directory where you have unpacked eXist.
Then issue the command

bin/startup.sh or bin/startup.bat

depending on your operating system. 


